ELBERT V. POPPELL and FREDDIE DAVIS v. THE STATE OF FLORIDA. 14 So. (2nd) 903

June Term, 1943

July 27, 1943 En Banc Rehearing Denied September 20, 1943. Davis, Davis & McClure, Walter S. Blanton and W. P. Chavous, for appellants. J. Tom Watson, Attorney General, Woodrow M. Melvin and John C. Wynn, Assistant Attorneys General, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

Affirmed.

BUFORD, C. J., CHAPMAN, THOMAS, ADAMS and SEBRING, JJ., concur. TERRELL and BROWN, JJ., dissent.
